'''Dr. Pinosky''' is a surgical resident at [[Seattle Grace Hospital]]. He worked with [[Preston Burke]] on [[Elizabeth Fallon]].

==History==
Dr. Preston Burke called his name to turn off the ECG monitor after Liz Fallon died.

==Career==
He is a surgical resident at [[Seattle Grace Hospital]].

==Notes and Trivia==
*He is uncredited for the episode he appears in.
